<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Aigralys - Agentic AI for Complex Digital Ecosystems</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Aigralys: Sistemas de IA Agéntica para ecosistemas digitales complejos. Especialización en agroindustria y operaciones de alta complejidad.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --grafito: #1C1C1E;
      --grafito-light: #2d2d3a;
      --off-white: #F8F9FA;
      --teal: #00B3A4;
      --teal-dark: #009688;
      --cyan: #00CFFF;
      --oliva: #7DA453;
      --border: rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.15);
      --glow: rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.3);
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: var(--grafito);
      color: var(--off-white);
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .bg-animation {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.4;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(125, 164, 83, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 40% 20%, rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 40%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .grid-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 1;
      background-image: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 50px 50px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .floating-shapes {
      position: fixed;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .shape {
      position: absolute;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    .shape-1 {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      top: 10%;
      right: 10%;
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }

    .shape-2 {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      bottom: 20%;
      left: 15%;
      animation-delay: 5s;
    }

    .shape-3 {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      top: 60%;
      right: 20%;
      animation-delay: 10s;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
      25% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-40px) rotate(-5deg); }
      75% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg); }
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      z-index: 1000;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .brand-logo {
      height: 45px;
      width: auto;
    }

    .brand-text {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--cyan) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      list-style: none;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.8);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      position: relative;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--teal);
      transition: width 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--teal);
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .lang-switch {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--off-white);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      font-family: inherit;
    }

    .lang-switch:hover {
      border-color: var(--teal);
      background: rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--glow);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 12rem 3rem 8rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-logo {
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      display: block;
      width: 200px;
      height: auto;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px var(--glow));
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--cyan);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--off-white) 0%, var(--teal) 60%, var(--cyan) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }

    .hero h1 .highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan) 0%, var(--teal) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .recognition-bar {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .recognition-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .recognition-number {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--cyan) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .recognition-label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.6);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    section {
      padding: 6rem 3rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    section.tight {
      padding: 5rem 3rem;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--off-white) 0%, var(--teal) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.7);
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .domains-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .domain-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.05) 0%, rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.8) 100%);
      padding: 3rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.4s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .domain-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--cyan) 50%, var(--oliva) 100%);
      transform: scaleX(0);
      transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform 0.4s;
    }

    .domain-card:hover::before {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }

    .domain-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      border-color: var(--teal);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.2);
    }

    .domain-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--teal);
    }

    .domain-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .domain-list li {
      padding-left: 1.8rem;
      position: relative;
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.8);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .domain-list li::before {
      content: '▸';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--oliva);
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .focus-areas {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(125, 164, 83, 0.08) 0%, rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.05) 100%);
      padding: 6rem 3rem;
      margin: 4rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .focus-container {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .focus-intro {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.8);
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .applications-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .app-card {
      background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.6);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(125, 164, 83, 0.2);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--oliva);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .app-card:hover {
      transform: translateX(8px);
      border-left-color: var(--teal);
      background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.8);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(125, 164, 83, 0.2);
    }

    .app-card h3 {
      color: var(--oliva);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .app-card p {
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.75);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .insights-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .insight-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.4s;
      position: relative;
    }

    .insight-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--cyan) 100%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.4s;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .insight-card:hover::after {
      opacity: 0.05;
    }

    .insight-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: var(--cyan);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0, 207, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .insight-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      background: rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.15);
      color: var(--cyan);
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .insight-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--teal);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .insight-text {
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.75);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .connect {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 6rem 3rem;
    }

    .connect h2 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--off-white) 0%, var(--teal) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .connect-text {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .footer-profile {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .profile-thumb {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid var(--teal);
      object-fit: cover;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 179, 164, 0.3);
    }

    .linkedin-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--teal-dark) 100%);
      color: var(--grafito);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      border: 2px solid var(--teal);
    }

    .linkedin-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 50px var(--glow);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 3rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.4);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
      }
      .domains-grid,
      .applications-grid,
      .insights-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-container {
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .hero {
        padding: 10rem 1.5rem 6rem;
      }
      .hero-logo {
        width: 150px;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
      }
      .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      .recognition-bar {
        gap: 2.5rem;
      }
      .recognition-number {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }
      section {
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-animation"></div>
  <div class="grid-overlay"></div>
  <div class="floating-shapes">
    <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
    <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
    <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-container">
        <div class="brand">
          <img src="./assets/logo.png" alt="Aigralys" class="brand-logo">
          <span class="brand-text">Aigralys</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="#agentic" class="nav-text">IA Agéntica</a></li>
          <li><a href="#agro" class="nav-text">Agroindustria</a></li>
          <li><a href="#dominios" class="nav-text">Dominios</a></li>
          <li><a href="#practica" class="nav-text">Práctica</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contacto" class="nav-text">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="lang-switch" onclick="toggleLanguage()">EN</button>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
      <img src="./assets/logo.png" alt="Aigralys" class="hero-logo">
      <div class="hero-badge hero-badge-text">Agentic AI · Digital Ecosystems</div>
      <h1><span class="highlight">IA Agéntica</span> para Ecosistemas Digitales Complejos</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle hero-subtitle-text">
        Aigralys documenta prácticas de diseño, implementación y gobernanza de sistemas agénticos de IA aplicados a transformación operativa en industrias de alta complejidad, con especialización en agroindustria.
      </p>
      <div class="recognition-bar">
        <div class="recognition-item">
          <div class="recognition-number">20+</div>
          <div class="recognition-label recog-label-1">Años en IT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="recognition-item">
          <div class="recognition-number">AI</div>
          <div class="recognition-label recog-label-2">Agéntica</div>
        </div>
        <div class="recognition-item">
          <div class="recognition-number">AGRO</div>
          <div class="recognition-label recog-label-3">Focus</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="agentic" class="tight">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-1">Qué es IA Agéntica</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle section-subtitle-1">
          Sistemas de IA capaces de tomar decisiones autónomas, ejecutar acciones y coordinar con otros agentes para lograr objetivos complejos en entornos operativos reales. No son chatbots: son agentes que actúan.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="domains-grid">
        <div class="domain-card">
          <h3 class="domain-title domain-title-1">Autonomía Supervisada</h3>
          <ul class="domain-list">
            <li class="domain-li-1">Agentes que toman decisiones operativas dentro de límites definidos</li>
            <li class="domain-li-2">Escalamiento inteligente a humanos cuando se requiere expertise</li>
            <li class="domain-li-3">Aprendizaje continuo desde feedback y resultados medidos</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="domain-card">
          <h3 class="domain-title domain-title-2">Orquestación Multi-agente</h3>
          <ul class="domain-list">
            <li class="domain-li-4">Coordinación entre agentes especializados por función</li>
            <li class="domain-li-5">Protocolos de handoff y colas de trabajo distribuidas</li>
            <li class="domain-li-6">Resiliencia operativa ante fallas individuales</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="domain-card">
          <h3 class="domain-title domain-title-3">Integración con Ecosistemas</h3>
          <ul class="domain-list">
            <li class="domain-li-7">Conexión con ERPs, CRMs, sistemas legacy y telemetría IoT</li>
            <li class="domain-li-8">Decisiones en tiempo real sobre datos distribuidos</li>
            <li class="domain-li-9">Trazabilidad completa de acciones y razonamiento</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="agro" class="focus-areas">
      <div class="focus-container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title section-title-2">IA Agéntica en Agroindustria</h2>
          <p class="focus-intro focus-intro-text">
            La agroindustria es uno de los contextos más exigentes para sistemas agénticos: decisiones en tiempo real con datos climáticos, edáficos, de mercado, logística y cumplimiento normativo. Desde campo hasta despacho, los agentes orquestan complejidad operativa crítica.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="applications-grid">
          <div class="app-card">
            <h3 class="app-title-1">Planificación Operativa</h3>
            <p class="app-text-1">Agentes que orquestan decisiones de siembra, riego y cosecha integrando clima, suelo, mercados y recursos en tiempo real.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <h3 class="app-title-2">Trazabilidad End-to-End</h3>
            <p class="app-text-2">Monitoreo de insumos, lotes, transporte y almacenamiento con alertas automáticas ante desviaciones y cumplimiento normativo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <h3 class="app-title-3">Optimización Logística</h3>
            <p class="app-text-3">Coordinación multi-agente para cosecha, transporte y acopio con optimización dinámica de rutas y asignación de recursos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <h3 class="app-title-4">Gestión de Riesgos</h3>
            <p class="app-text-4">Evaluación continua de riesgos climáticos, fitosanitarios y de mercado con simulación de escenarios y respuestas automáticas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <h3 class="app-title-5">Copilotos Operativos</h3>
            <p class="app-text-5">Asistentes agénticos para equipos de campo, finanzas y compras con acceso contextual y ejecución de tareas rutinarias.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app-card">
            <h3 class="app-title-6">Integración Legacy</h3>
            <p class="app-text-6">Wrappers agénticos para conectar sistemas existentes (ERPs, sensores IoT) sin refundaciones costosas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="dominios">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-3">Dominios Técnicos</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle section-subtitle-2">
          Áreas de práctica en arquitectura, implementación y gobernanza de sistemas agénticos.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="insights-grid">
